data.description: Introducing this charming family home in highly sought after Hollister California.  Beautifully situated in a cul-du-sac on a spacious 9,967 square foot lot. This 1950's-style gem features 2 bedrooms with walk-in closets, unique bath fixtures, and a cozy kitchen with built-in display cabinets. Enjoy gatherings in the open dining area with a wood fireplace and French doors leading to the back patio with pergola and brick fireplace. With a 2-car garage, side yard entrance, and ample space for RV parking, entertaining is easy. Located in the Hollister Elementary and San Benito High School districts, and just 4 minutes from downtown amenities. Don't wait, schedule a viewing today this property won't last long!
